
- Do not use bcopy(). use memset ('0') for portability.
- Do not use u8.
- use assert() rather than perror & abort.
- find_key_by_fd is completely wrong... (must p=p->next; in the loop)
- do not use label and goto.

- <openssl/sha.h> is not necessary in lib/horus_key.c since <horus.h>
  will include it depending upon the result in config.h
- do not use malloc, vectorx, or any other heavy task in lib/horus_key.c


- the method for debugging: sh ./libtool --mode=execute gdb horus-file

